cribe only actions of your character)</strong></span>\"</p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 210, 119);\">⋆</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 210, 119);\"><strong>Example:</strong></span> \"(OOC: Disregard the previous scenario. Write a new starting message for our roleplay—Vasily gets involved in some trouble with some yakuza while he's wandering around. I will be playing as my character myself, so describe only actions of your character)\"</p><p></p><hr><p></p><p class=\"css-1bntj9o css-ksvjqq\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(255, 210, 119);\">★ 𝐀𝐔𝐓𝐇𝐎𝐑'𝐒 𝐍𝐎𝐓𝐄</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(255, 210, 119);\">⋆</span><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text);\"> <em>Probably it'd be a good idea to reinforce his muteness through the prompt, unfortunately LLMs often struggle with such concepts</em></span></p><hr><p></p><p class=\"css-1bntj9o css-ksvjqq\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(255, 210, 119);\">★ 𝐎𝐓𝐇𝐄𝐑 𝐆𝐊 𝐁𝐎𝐓𝐒</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"div Btn pp-pg-total .css-y9k5u7\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/789d2eea-806b-4088-9b48-02dbf407f31f_character-ogata-hyakunosuke\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 210, 119);\"><strong>◦ 🔫 ◦ 𝐎𝐠𝐚𝐭𝐚 𝐇𝐲𝐚𝐤𝐮𝐧𝐨𝐬𝐮𝐤𝐞 ◦ 🐾 ◦</strong></span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"div Btn pp-pg-total .css-y9k5u7\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/28b90cdd-6828-417f-a32e-aaaff2fabc9f_character-sugimoto-saichi\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 210, 119);\"><strong>◦ 🧣 ◦ 𝐒𝐮𝐠𝐢𝐦𝐨𝐭𝐨 𝐒𝐚𝐢𝐜𝐡𝐢 ◦ 🍲 ◦</strong></span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"div Btn pp-pg-total .css-y9k5u7\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/067a8840-3230-4b8c-b76c-5235ce5af20d_character-shiraishi-yo